Title: Laugh
Artist: OY Tai

The Enso represents the way of Zen as a circle of vast space, lacking nothing and holding nothing in excess.  It represents form and emptiness, void and fullness.

Drawn in one fluid, expressive stroke, the enso represents the state of mind of the artist . As the brush trails off into nothingness, leaving an open circle, it is also the acceptance of imperfection as it is. 

The enso circle is born from emptiness. However its center is full of potency and infinite possibility.  On this particular piece, inside the circle is the calligraphy for "Laugh".  

If you are looking for an enso circle without words, see the following listing:
https://www.etsy.com/ca/listing/400995465/original-enso-painting-option-for-custom?ref=shop_home_active_22

Hand painted with chinese ink on acid free 60 lb paper measuring 8" x 10". This is an original, not a print. Certificate of Authenticity included. 
 
My art has been exhibited internationally and I am a premiere member of the International Chinese Calligraphy and Ink Painting Society. Artist's website: oystudio.com

All my art is created here in my studio in Canada, and shipped worldwide.

Frame and matting not included. The easiest way to frame an irregular sized artwork is to use a float frame. Simply insert the artwork between the two panes of glass with no matting or mounting necessary. You can buy them at Michaels, Walmart, etc . Carnelian is a high energy stone that is great for stress release. It is a powerful stabilizing stone that provides gentle soothing energy. It helps restore vitality and motivation while releasing stress. Carnelian is also a well-known fertility stone. Made with love and positive thoughts, this wrist mala has twenty-one 8 mm high quality natural smooth round carnelian stones in many shades and hues of orange, yellow and tangerine. Each beautiful carnelian has its own unique shade that is almost translucent in the light. 

I accented the beautiful carnelians with two 6 mm sterling silver round beads and a silver-plated charm with the inscriptions "Live Laugh Love" to bring out the rich colour of the carnelians and to add significance. This eye-catching carnelian mala is perfect for stress release, emotional balance and motivation. It will help soothe and lift the spirit.  The size of the stones makes this bracelet suitable for (stacking) wearing with other bracelets. You can use it for meditation, mantras, counting or whenever you need something for stress release and to restore energy and motivation.

The lead-free, nickel-free silver-plated charm measures approximately 19 mm in diameter. It is strung on three sterling silver rings. This beautiful charm has the inscription " Live Laugh Love" on one side of the charm, the other side depicts the pattern of the sun's rays. 

This wrist mala measures approximately 7.3" or 18.5 cm and is strung on two strong stretch cords for durability.  It will fit comfortably for a wrist with a circumference of 6 to 7 inches, depending on whether you prefer a snug or loose fit. Please convo me or simply note in "note to seller" at time of order if you need a diiferent size. Please note that bead count will change once the size is adjusted. 

About Malas: 
Malas are sets of prayer beads that are used to keep your mind spiritually focused while reciting or mentally repeating a mantra. Mala is an ancient Sanskrit term meaning “garland”. Malas are the traditional and spiritual tools of the Buddhist and Hindu religions. The strings of beads are worn over the hand or in the hand so that each bead can be counted as each prayer is recited. It is also a wonderful accessory in meditation or as “worry beads”.

These files can be used with vector software (such as Adobe Illustrator), Silhouette, and Cricut machines, and other machines - please ensure that your machine is able to load one of the four file types before purchasing. If you have Silhouette Basic (not Designer Edition) you will need to use the DXF version of the file. SVG file formats are not supported on Silhouette Studio basic. PNGs are not vector-based and therefore the cut lines are not as accurate. Utilize the other formats where possible. 

Designs will come in gray or black unless otherwise shown in the flat (IE, not a finished product) mockup photo. The finished product mockup photos are for demonstration purposes only. These designs are intended for craft cutting and while they CAN be used as printable files, we do not offer color changes, assistance, or troubleshooting for printing.

Designs do not include any personalization.

** PLEASE NOTE: The ZIP file will be the designs only, no watermarks, backgrounds, or Trí Déag Designs Logos will be attached. They will be ready to use, provided that your machine and/or software is compatible. **


**** DIGITAL FILE ****

This is a digital file only. No physical item will be mailed and therefore no refunds will be given. We will do our best to assist with troubleshooting, but it is our customer's responsibility to make sure their software is compatible with the provided file types. 

** PLEASE NOTE: Our designs are not very intricate in nature, but due to thin cutting areas, they are not suitable for vinyl on drinkware or other small die-cut designs. results.description:
This is a laser printed waterslide for use on a tumbler, or glass.  It will fit a 20 or 30oz tumbler. If you need a special size, please message me and we can work out a custom size.  The laser printed waterslide has no need to be coated before application.  You will apply this over an epoxied cup, then add one more layer of epoxy.

Waterslides are used to put full color designs on hard surfaces such as glass, wood, plastic, stainless steel, etc. They are called waterslides because you use water to slowly separate the image from the paper backing for application (similar to a temporary tattoo). These are not to be used for fabric application.
